	<h1 class="title">美国拍了不少“总统剧”，画风和待遇还挺不一样的</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">彭卡茜 </span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2015-12-23 10:58:33 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/19548/medium/19548.jpg?1450796452" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


